{"tid":499931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"姚松炎倡申請緊急禁制令，法夢認同可行","createTime":"2017-12-15T10:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T05:49:11.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1b2c91366f68787421ce6c6b8639e6ebf576eb","tid":499931,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:34:55.000Z","msg":"12月14日，姚松炎在其直播頻道，與法夢成員「腸腸」討論修改議事規則。<br />\n<br />\n「腸腸」指一旦遂建制所願，修訂或違反基本法第 75 條和附件二。「成個制度會徹底改變，而且唔知會變成點，影響好深遠。」<br />\n<br />\n姚松炎提議民主派，可嘗試申請緊急禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n法夢成員「腸腸」然其說。迄今已經有相當多法律學者，指出修訂涉違基本法。法庭不應迴避爭議，有受理的法律基礎。<br />\n<br />\n直播重溫：<a href=\"http://goo.gl/YjBYxD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FYjBYxD&d=49Z45uPvrCJedagPJ%2FldkC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1b985ed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goo.gl/YjBYxD</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/姚松炎倡申請緊急禁制令-法夢認同可行/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%A7%9A%E6%9D%BE%E7%82%8E%E5%80%A1%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%A6%81%E5%88%B6%E4%BB%A4-%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%A2%E8%AA%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%2F&d=49Z45uPvrCJedagPJ%2FldkC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=cb2f5272\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%A7%9A%E6%9D%BE%E7%82%8E%E5%80%A1%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%A6%81%E5%88%B6%E4%BB%A4-%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%A2%E8%AA%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%2F&h=300a59a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/姚松炎倡申請緊急禁制令-法夢認同可行/</a>"},{"pid":"5559fc4dd805fdd05f3efc15f4458cd77fbe3834","tid":499931,"uid":52638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be6720f3002113e83045abb6aeaad61517ee967","tid":499931,"uid":52638,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"無力回天了"},{"pid":"905c95418d08d84453fa92024dde567f643c98c4","tid